Dae-Jang Gong, aka Raid Leader, used to be rank one in the worlds first VR RPG game Rou Online, but now hes trapped in a game called Astrom as an NPC due to the evil scheming of an AI! Now, Dae-Jang must find a way to escape this sick metaverse, but will he be able to outsmart artificial intelligence?
(Source: WEBTOONS, edited)

Zephyr is the last human fighting evil in a world abandoned by the gods. When he is killed in battle by Tartarus, the god of destruction, all hope for humanity seems lost. But Zephyrs fate is not sealed the gods who find his battles entertaining have gifted him a second chance at life, as he is sent ten years into the past, back to when he was a slave instead of the most powerful human alive. Can Zephyr get his revenge against Tartarus and save the woman he loves, or is he doomed to repeat the past? (Source: WEBTOONS)
